                    <th>
                        <h1>Muş Köftesi</h1>
<hr>
                            <a href="file:///C:/Users/saygi/Desktop/Hez%20Dolmas%C4%B1.html" target="_self">Hez Dolması</a>| 
                            <a href="file:///C:/Users/saygi/Desktop/Helima%C5%9F%C4%B1%20%C3%87orbas%C4%B1.html" target="_self">Helimaşı Çorbası</a>|
                            <a href="file:///C:/Users/saygi/Desktop/Mu%C5%9F%20B%C3%B6re%C4%9Fi.html"  target="_self">Muş Böreği</a>|
